data.name: AutoPropertyDescription
data.value: Networked properties must be implemented as an auto property for them to function. Init setters do not count
data.comment: An optional longer localizable description of the diagnostic.

data.name: AutoPropertyMessageFormat
data.value: Networked properties must be implemented as an auto property { get; set; }
data.comment: The format-able message the diagnostic displays.

data.name: AutoPropertyTitle
data.value: Networked properties must be auto-implemented { get; set; }
data.comment: The title of the diagnostic.

data.name: ChangeMissingDescription
data.value: The change callback method must exist on the type as the name is defined or defaulted to. If default, it will look for "On[PropertyName]Changed"
data.comment: An optional longer localizable description of the diagnostic.

data.name: ChangeMissingMessageFormat
data.value: The change callback method '{0}' does not exist
data.comment: The format-able message the diagnostic displays.

data.name: ChangeMissingTitle
data.value: Change callback method is missing
data.comment: The title of the diagnostic.

data.name: ChangeParameterCountDescription
data.value: The change callback must have two parameters. The first containing the old value; the second containing the new value
data.comment: An optional longer localizable description of the diagnostic.

data.name: ChangeParameterCountMessageFormat

data.name: ChangeParameterCountTitle

data.comment: The title of the diagnostic.
